Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.20,0:00:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Grand\NEquestria Pony Summit!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.52,0:00:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You delegates have\Ntraveled far and wide
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.92,0:00:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to represent your cities
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.52,0:00:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,as we seek to\Ncelebrate and learn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.66,0:00:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,from all the unique places
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.21,0:00:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,that make up our wonderful\Nland of Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.33,0:00:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,At tonight's welcome\Nreception, Princess Cadance
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.19,0:00:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,will dedicate this beautiful\Nfriendship statue,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.94,0:00:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,made up of gemstones from\Neach of your home cities.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.24,0:00:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'd like to\Nturn things over
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.81,0:00:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,to the one who\Norganized the Summit,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.03,0:00:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess\NTwilight Sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.74,0:01:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.58,0:01:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,With delegates from\Nover fifty cities
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.69,0:01:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,attending three days of\Nconferences, receptions,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and meetings,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.62,0:01:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the largest Grand\NEquestria Pony Summit yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.13,0:01:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And let me tell you,\Nputting it all together
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.24,0:01:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,has led to more than one\Nsleepless night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.04,0:01:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We're so excited to have you\Nhere and to learn more
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.21,0:01:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,about life all across this\Ngreat land of ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.74,0:01:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, my faithful\Nassistant Spike
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.47,0:01:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,would like to say\Na few words.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.80,0:01:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, hello, everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.15,0:01:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here to help any way I can,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.75,0:01:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,so if there's anything I\Ncan do for any of you--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.04,0:01:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We love you,\NPrincess Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.16,0:01:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We love all the princesses!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.12,0:01:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess everypony\Nloves a princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.62,0:02:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Regular subtitles by YayPonies\NWe have muffins!\Nhttp://yayponies.eu/
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.54,0:02:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.88,0:02:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.84,0:02:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Little help?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.53,0:02:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, we need you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.37,0:02:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! What\Ncan I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.01,0:02:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike: Whoa! What\Nhappened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.29,0:02:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry, Spike, I just
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.75,0:02:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,need a quick nap...napkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.17,0:03:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell the delegates I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been awake three straight\Ndays preparing for the Summit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to make sure she\Ngets some rest today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.98,0:03:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll never be able to\Nattend the welcome reception
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.19,0:03:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,in this condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.94,0:03:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I count on you to see to\Nit that she isn't disturbed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.41,0:03:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise I won't let you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.66,0:03:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.58,0:03:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Not on my watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.84,0:03:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you keep it\Ndown a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.81,0:04:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you\Nbirdseed...worms...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Just please stop singing\Nbefore you wake the Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.76,0:04:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. I can't believe\Nthat worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, hi fellas. Sorry\Nto break up your game,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's sort\Nof an important
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.57,0:04:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,diplomatic summit\Nkinda thingy going on
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.59,0:04:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and it involves a princess\Nneeding to sleep and uh,...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe you could move\Nyour game somewhere else?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The Princess thanks you\Nfor your understanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.36,0:04:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have to do\Nthis right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,HA-CHEW!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:04:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:04:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Are those Dragonsneeze Trees?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.33,0:05:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,These are too top heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.20,0:05:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't take much to\Nbring these beauties down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.94,0:05:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you just wait a few hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, it's a public hazard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got my orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.86,0:05:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've got my\Norders, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,from Princess Twi-Twi-Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,HA-CHEW!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.24,0:05:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Why didn't you say so!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.52,0:05:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee, I reckon they'll\Nkeep a few more hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Good thing I've got the\Nprincesses on my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.32,0:05:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.04,0:05:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,EXCUSE ME!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,EXCUSE ME! SIR!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.47,0:05:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I REALLY NEED YOU TO--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.93,0:05:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,--STOP RIGHT NOW!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.13,0:05:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.77,0:05:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me guess, the noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.98,0:05:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but we can't have\Na broken water main.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.71,0:05:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you couldn't\Ndo this yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.00,0:05:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, pal, I'm just tryin'\Nto make sure everything
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.36,0:05:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,runs smooth for the Summit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.13,0:05:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is no Summit\Nwithout Princess Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.72,0:06:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And she needs things to\Nbe kept quiet around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.78,0:06:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you don't mind, I'd--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.94,0:06:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, all right, if that's\Nhow she wants it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But if something happens,\Nit ain't my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. Princess Twilight\Nwill be rested;
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.70,0:06:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Cadance will be proud
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and Princess Spike\Ndeserves a little reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Spike. Heh-heh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.15,0:06:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I worked\Nforever on this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.82,0:06:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, hi, can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.21,0:06:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,My friend here, the\Ndistinguished pony
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,from up Manehattan and I are\Nin a bit of a pickle,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.37,0:06:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and we need the Princess\NTwilight to resolve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.71,0:06:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you talk a little quieter?\NAnd maybe come back later?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.00,0:06:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sure now, gosh,\NI wish we could,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but uh, we're both\Nsupposed to give speeches
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,about our local economies\Nin five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And we've been booked\Nin the same hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.46,0:07:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the room first,\Nand let's be honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.50,0:07:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,my speech is more important.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Point of order there, sir,\Nbut I think you'll find
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.94,0:07:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that my speech is the more\Nimportant one, dontcha know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, youse is gonna have\Na lot of unhappy delegates
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.19,0:07:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,on your hooves unless\Nwe get a ruling
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,from Princess\NTwilight right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see what I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.77,0:07:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Does something\Nneed scheduling?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.80,0:07:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.51,0:07:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Two delegates have speeches\Nbooked in the same hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.92,0:07:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Just put the hay in the\Napple and eat the candle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.93,0:07:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I need an answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.11,0:07:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But Twilight can't\Neven think straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.81,0:07:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh! What am\NI supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? What did she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.34,0:08:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She picked me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.64,0:08:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey hey hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.70,0:08:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not be too\Nhasty there, good sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a feeling\Nshe went with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey if she\Ndidn't pick me,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,it ain't hard to see that as an\Ninsult to all of Manehattan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.79,0:08:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm sayin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And it'd sure be a\Nshame to see something
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.99,0:08:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,like a scheduling issue\Ncreate a nasty old rift
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,between Whinnyapolis\Nand Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.72,0:08:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So? What did the\NPrincess say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.41,0:08:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on now,\Nspit it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.54,0:08:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ummm, she said that,\Nwell, she said, that she,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.77,0:08:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,she wants you to ... share it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's what the Princess\Nwants, what are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The Princess is always right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No hard feelings; this\Nis not about you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.32,0:08:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And now back to more\Nimportant things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:09:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Combining those two\Ntalks was a disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.78,0:09:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The hall was overcrowded
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.07,0:09:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and the speakers just\Nshouted over each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.11,0:09:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.15,0:09:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would the Princess\Nhave made such a decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.64,0:09:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.12,0:09:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, by order of Princess\NTwilight...be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really looking forward
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.39,0:09:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,to the "Don't Spend\NAll Your Bits" speech,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.89,0:09:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but when I went into the\Nhall, a pony had taken my seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A pony who used to be my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Your friend took\Nyour seat? Big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.13,0:09:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No offense, but I don't need\Nsome random dragon's opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.53,0:09:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to hear what\NPrincess Twilight thinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh. Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.06,0:09:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, the Princess says no\Nfriendship should end
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:09:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,over a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.30,0:09:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You should forgive your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! Oh, the\NPrincess is so wise!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.42,0:10:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I could tell these\Ndelegates anything
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,as long as they think it\Ncame from Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, who's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So how can Princess\NTwilight be of service?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.12,0:11:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well! As host city, the\NCanterlot delegation
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.56,0:11:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,feels it's only right\Nthat we should get passes
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.32,0:11:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to every meeting\Nand party, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's doesn't seem fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.25,0:11:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, Princess Twilight\Ndoesn't think that seems fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.13,0:11:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.09,0:11:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It was worth a try,\Nthough, wasn't it old chap?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.25,0:11:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.81,0:11:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I just took care of a\Nwhole bunch of stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that Twilight won't have to\Nworry about when she wakes up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.86,0:11:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonder if anypony else\Nneeds the Princess's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.02,0:11:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can check a few\Nof these meetings
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.66,0:11:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,off Twilight's schedule,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.25,0:11:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,then when she wakes up,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,she won't have to think about\Nanything but the reception.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.04,0:11:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, says here you have a\Nmeeting with Princess Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuppers. She wanted\Nme to prep her on all the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.60,0:11:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,different gemstones in the\NCitizens of Equestria statue
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,before the reception tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.63,0:12:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, well, I'd rather um,\Ntell the Princess directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if it helps, you can\Ncall me Princess Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No no no! It's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The Princess asked me to take\Ncare of a few things for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I came to find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.96,0:12:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The Princess says so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, let's start with topaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.13,0:12:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here for your 2:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.19,0:12:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.19,0:12:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm supposed to be\Nbriefing Princess Twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.54,0:12:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,on the progress with\Nthe water main.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.46,0:12:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I speak for the Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.31,0:12:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, uh, can I start\Nfixing it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.70,0:12:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gettin' a little\Nworried, to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.21,0:12:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, Twilight still needs\Nher rest and her "no noise"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,policy is still in effect\Nfor a few more hours. Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.22,0:12:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Spike, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.52,0:12:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you know, just settin'\Nem up and knockin' em down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.85,0:12:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.01,0:13:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only have I kept things\Nquiet so Twilight could sleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.37,0:13:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I also took care of all her\Nafternoon meetings
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.33,0:13:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,so she won't have to worry\Nabout them when she wakes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.58,0:13:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure she'd\Nwant you doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.19,0:13:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There are so many things to\Nkeep track of at this Summit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.94,0:13:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, don't worry,\NI got it covered.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.38,0:13:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I know Twilight so well, it's\Neasy to make decisions like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.13,0:13:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.13,0:13:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you for keeping\NTwilight's stress level down...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...as long as that's the\Nreal reason you're doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.42,0:13:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, why else\Nwould I be doing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not enjoying speaking\Nfor Twilight a little bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.84,0:13:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoying it? Ha ha! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The only things I'm doing\Nby order of the Princess
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,are for the good of the Summit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.67,0:13:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh heh heh heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.40,0:13:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,By order of the Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.88,0:14:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,By order of the Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.84,0:14:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,By order of the Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.30,0:14:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. Princess life is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.03,0:14:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure is. But it's also\Nhard work, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.37,0:14:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, it's not so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.97,0:14:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, I'm concerned you might\Nbe abusing your relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,with Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NI'm a great princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.17,0:14:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, Twilight's\Na great princess
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.00,0:14:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and I've been working\Nhard to help her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.86,0:14:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,When two delegates\Nhad a falling out,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who fixed\Ntheir friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.28,0:14:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I listened to that pony\Ndrone on about gems
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,for forty-five minutes so\NTwilight wouldn't have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.53,0:14:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I moved a polo match away from\Nthe tower so she could sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.22,0:14:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And I didn't even eat that\Ndelicious looking statue!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.92,0:14:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a decision-making master!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, so maybe I did get a little\Ncarried away making decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:15:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not like\Nanything bad happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.44,0:15:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Whooooaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.94,0:15:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.05,0:15:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go shut off the main;\Nyou get rid of the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,At least the statue's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.12,0:16:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...Ah...HACHEW!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, bless me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.18,0:16:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.78,0:16:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.74,0:16:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, uh, ya see, there\Nwas this polo game and--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.81,0:16:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you let\Na water main burst
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.87,0:16:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,on Canterlot's most\Nimportant day?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.05,0:16:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.37,0:16:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Twilight said\Nto stop working on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.27,0:16:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what about these trees?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.88,0:16:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I ordered them trimmed to\Navoid just such a situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.89,0:16:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the princess\Ntold me to stop, bub.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.25,0:16:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would the Princess make\Nsuch horrible decisions?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.14,0:16:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This all could have\Nbeen prevented!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.71,0:16:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Everypony, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.02,0:16:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry all this happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.07,0:17:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you apologizing for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.63,0:17:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,These were Princess\NTwilight's awful decisions!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.09,0:17:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm about to blow my stack\Non Princess Twilight,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.99,0:17:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you that for nothin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.15,0:17:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.14,0:17:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll not let Princess Twilight\Ngive Canterlot a bad name
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,in the eyes of Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.86,0:17:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, everypony, let's go\Ngive her a piece of our mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.19,0:17:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you've got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.93,0:17:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,WAIT!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean... wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.52,0:17:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an angry mob here\Nthat demands satisfaction!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.51,0:17:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.71,0:17:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,we don't want to wake\Nthe Princess, do we?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.63,0:17:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake her? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.07,0:17:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're tellin' me\Nthat she's asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.37,0:17:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess! We must speak at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:18:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,SHE... IS...SLEEPING!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.12,0:18:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're here, Spike.\NWe've got a lot to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.17,0:18:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know if the\Nwater main was fixed?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, you seem well rested.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.11,0:18:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't slept like\Nthat since I was a filly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.80,0:18:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, at least I\Ngot one thing right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was the one thing\NCadance asked of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I did do a good job today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.49,0:18:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Fancy Pants. What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.60,0:18:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play games\Nwith me, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.78,0:18:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You know why I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.23,0:18:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this about the special\Nprivileges you wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.76,0:18:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Because this seems\Na little extreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.30,0:18:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Special privileges?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.40,0:18:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The last thing on my mind\Nis special privileges!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on, Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.34,0:18:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...you needed to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:18:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And Princess Cadance told me\Nyou weren't to be disturbed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And there was this bird,\Nand well...long story short,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.58,0:19:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a few decisions\Non your behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.30,0:19:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"A few decisions?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.43,0:19:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe more than a few.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.73,0:19:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But I had good\Nintentions. Honest!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.89,0:19:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Until I didn't anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.39,0:19:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.94,0:19:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I got a\Nlittle carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.56,0:19:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It just felt so good to have\Nponies caring about my opinions
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,on such important matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I was just enjoying\Nfeeling like a princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.60,0:19:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Spike, one of the most\Nimportant things a princess
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.48,0:19:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,can do is realize when she's\Nmade a mistake and fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.23,0:19:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.58,0:19:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You could start with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.24,0:19:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, hi there, everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.90,0:19:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So I guess I owe you all\Na pretty big apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.48,0:19:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's funny, here we\Nare at a Summit
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.19,0:20:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that brings together ponies\Nfrom all across Equestria
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.44,0:20:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and all I could think\Nabout was myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You all came here to celebrate\Nthe things that make
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.22,0:20:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,each of our cities so\Nunique and special.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.17,0:20:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But instead of getting\Ninto the spirit of things
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.83,0:20:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,like all of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.42,0:20:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I used my friend's position\Nto make myself feel good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.95,0:20:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The Canterlot ruby\Ngoes here, old sport.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.70,0:20:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And ours goes\Nhere, dontcha know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.12,0:20:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this mean you forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.82,0:20:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.26,0:21:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You know the whole idea of the\Nstatue is that when each of us
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.25,0:21:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,plays our own small part, it\Nadds up to somethin' grand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.42,0:21:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite! Just like\Nhow all our cities
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.90,0:21:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,make up the beautiful\Nland of Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.73,0:21:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I hereby dedicate the\NCitizens of Equestria statue
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.14,0:21:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,to everypony who\Nplays their part,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.93,0:21:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter how big or\Nhow small.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.64,0:21:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.26,0:21:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...ah...ahhhh--
